oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville in Napa (2009)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Lindsey, Hillary; Murphy, David Lee; Randall, Jon; Rutherford, Rivers; Woodcuts (prints); Musical instruments; Guitar;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Nashville in Napa at the Baldacci Family Vineyards on August 1. Event features songwriters: Jim "Moose" Brown, Hillary Lindsey, David Lee Murphy, Jon Randall, Rivers Rutherford, and Don Sampson. Poster features woodcuts of a guitar, grapes, and music notes.
